Jenna Leigh Green https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jenna_Leigh_Green 0 Jennifer Leigh Green (born August 22, 1974) is an American actress and singer best known for her performances as Libby Chessler on the television show Sabrina the Teenage Witch, as well as for roles on tour in the musical Wicked and later in the Broadway production.
